{"word":"Abib","slug":"abib","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Abib</b> <a href=\"#/H24\">H24</a> <br/> Called also Nisan.<br/> First month in the Jewish calendar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=2'>Exo 12:2</a><br/> Passover instituted and Israelites depart from Egypt in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=15'>Exo 23:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=1'>Deu 16:1</a><br/> Tabernacle set up in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=2'>Exo 40:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=17'>Exo 40:17</a><br/> Israelites arrive at the wilderness of Zin in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=1'>Num 20:1</a><br/> Enter Canaan in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=4&verse=19'>Jos 4:19</a><br/> Jordan's overflow in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=15'>1Ch 12:15</a>"}]}